&lt;h1 id="what-is-renunciation">What is Renunciation?&lt;a class="td-heading-self-link" href="#what-is-renunciation" aria-label="Heading self-link">&lt;/a>&lt;/h1>
&lt;p>In Sanskrit, there are two words: &lt;em>Sanyasa&lt;/em> and &lt;em>Tyaga&lt;/em>.&lt;br>
People in the English-speaking world think both mean renunciation.&lt;br>
They are related but not the same.&lt;br>
Here, I am talking about &lt;em>Tyaga&lt;/em>.&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>